{"title":"贵州新山歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"贵州新山歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说人力难胜天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁龙抽水上山癫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高坡旱地装满水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑你太阳空发癫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（天柱县）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高坡无路开条路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平地无水开条沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开路只望人来走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开沟只望水长流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（岑巩县）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把锄头半斤铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛上山坡气不歇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你打窝来我栽树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合作造林搞建设。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（农民刘名万）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳雀生来靠大坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲤鱼生来靠大河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要想农业机械化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全靠工人老大哥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（农民王发坤）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新打锄头亮光光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开条沟儿五里长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一股银水朝坡下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瘦土变成谷米仓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧犁用了几千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥脚越犁越更浅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双轮双铧犁过后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老土翻身见青天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（成文魁）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}